OL,3,CHorse expert found guilty of murdering
OL,4,Chusband at Devon home
OL,6,FA horse whisperer from Devon has been
OL,7,Ffound guilty of killing her husband by
OL,8,Fstabbing him in the back with a knife.
OL,10,FChristine Rawle, 69, killed Ian Rawle,
OL,11,F72, at their home in Braunton on 21
OL,12,FAugust 2022.
OL,14,FExeter Crown Court heard that Mr Rawle
OL,15,Fthen followed his wife of 29 years for
OL,16,Fa hundred yards telling her to remove
OL,17,Fthe knife, before collapsing and dying
OL,18,Ffrom the wound.
