OL,6,FProsecutors claimed the case was "as
OL,7,Fclear a case of murder as you are
OL,8,Flikely to find", and said Rawle
OL,9,Fattacked her husband in a "fit of
OL,10,Ftemper" during an argument about land
OL,11,Fat their #800,000 home.
OL,13,FThe court heard Rawle and her husband
OL,14,Fhad a dysfunctional marriage and
OL,15,Flikened them to the Roald Dahl
OL,16,Fcharacters The Twits.
